menu "P4Hub Configuration"

    config P4HUB_WIFI_SSID
        string "WiFi SSID"
        default ""
        help
            SSID of the WiFi network to join (same network as the Ableton Link
            session). Left empty in the repo — set it locally (menuconfig or a
            gitignored sdkconfig); do not commit credentials.

    config P4HUB_WIFI_PASSWORD
        string "WiFi Password"
        default ""
        help
            Password for the WiFi network. Set locally; do not commit.

endmenu
